{"tid":606430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家]花展偷花　阿伯遇記者即舉杖追打","createTime":"2018-03-26T12:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T14:06:21.000Z","uid":84633,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18a8a4ce5108a8dba69228871cca66838cd5e10b","tid":606430,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:58:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/171930/%E8%8A%B1%E5%8D%89%E5%B1%95%E5%AE%8C%E7%B5%90-%E6%B4%BE%E8%8A%B1%E8%AE%8A%E5%81%B7%E8%8A%B1-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%81%87%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F%E8%88%89%E6%89%8B%E6%9D%96%E4%BD%9C%E5%8B%A2%E8%BF%BD%E6%89%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F171930%2F%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%258D%2589%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%25AE%258C%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%2581%25B7%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%259D%2596%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%258B%25A2%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2589%2593&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=77c92c2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/171930/%E8%8A%B1%E5%8D%89%E5%B1%95%E5%AE%8C%E7%B5%90-%E6%B4%BE%E8%8A%B1%E8%AE%8A%E5%81%B7%E8%8A%B1-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%81%87%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F%E8%88%89%E6%89%8B%E6%9D%96%E4%BD%9C%E5%8B%A2%E8%BF%BD%E6%89%93</a><br />\n<br />\n花卉展昨日落幕，康文署安排今日在維多利亞公園近糖街入口，派發超過5000個大麗花盆栽，雖然派發過程大致順利，但不少市民疑偷花，隨手把公園其他花圃內，非用作派發的盆栽，當作免費花卉自行拿走，惟在場未有保安制止；記者追問下，對方更舉起拐杖作勢要打攝影記者。<br />\n<br />\n有市民將花圃內非派法盆栽拿走　作勢打記者<br />\n<br />\n有市民因花不美麗而感失落，但另一邊廂，卻有未有依從指示排隊取花的市民「高高興興」，直接把附近花圃，並非作派發用途、原本作為場館裝飾的盆栽直接拿走，雖然附近有場地保安，但未有阻止。<br />\n<br />\n其中，記者見有年老夫婦和家傭4人共帶走6個盆栽，用手推車運走，當中部份盆栽由花圃直接取走，即屬非用作派法盆栽。<br />\n<br />\n記者上前追問有隨意拿取盆栽的伯伯，問他是否知道「一人只能領取一盆？」、「是否知道擅自拿走場地盆栽是違法？」時，伯伯企圖阻止攝影記者拍攝，甚至舉起拐杖作勢要毆打記者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n老而不死是為賊"},{"pid":"26fb88f8de5a34d0ceed2aa9fba256474bb34325","tid":606430,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"d老野真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾廿歲人都唔化"},{"pid":"0aa4542cdd8959d41792849bf55704f664f1d0b6","tid":606430,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"15713fc809b1efcd03f20705ed675e86bba73d58","tid":606430,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死老賊"}]}